<v-card flex fluid>
  <form class="pa-4">
    <v-layout row wrap>
      <v-flex xs6>
        <v-text-field
          v-model="address"
          :rules="addressRules"
          label="Address"
          placeholder="Street, City, State ZIP"
          required
        ></v-text-field>
      </v-flex>

      <v-flex class="ml-5" xs1>
        <v-select
          :items="priorities"
          :rules="[v => !!v || 'Priority required']"
          label="Priority"
          required
          justify-center
        ></v-select>
      </v-flex>

      <v-flex class="ml-5" xs2>
        <v-text-field 
          v-model="victims"
          :rules="victimsRules"
          label="# of Victims"
          required
        ></v-text-field>
      </v-flex>
    </v-layout>

    <v-layout row wrap>
      <v-flex xs5>
        <v-text-field
          v-model="contactName"
          :rules="[v => !!v || 'Contact person\'s name is required']"
          label="Contact Name"
          required
        ></v-text-field>
      </v-flex>

      <v-flex class="ml-5" xs2>
        <v-text-field
          v-model="contactPhone"
          :rules="phoneRules"
          label="Phone Number"
          required
          justify-center
        ></v-text-field>
      </v-flex>
    </v-layout>

    <v-layout class="pt-3">
      <v-flex xs8>
        <v-textarea
          outline
          name="notes"
          label="Notes"
          class="ma-0"
        ></v-textarea>
      </v-flex>
    </v-layout>

    <v-card-actions>
      <v-spacer></v-spacer>
      <v-btn
        color="#A9A9A9"
      >Cancel</v-btn>
      <v-btn
        color="primary"
        class="ml-3"
      >Submit</v-btn>
    </v-card-actions>
  </form>
</v-card>
